channel.title: Mega Problem - - - Help if you can please. [at least look?]
channel.description: [center]Yea , you read right, I am asking for [b]your[/b] help for once. lol. :D well I am in the process of making a new client since my old webclient won't work and nobody will accept 350k to make me one out of a very basic 317 client with no sprites or models... Forget that though, I am finished editing my new client which has all the new items / gameframe / 377 cache. And I made a jar out of it. Now the jar loads [i]perfectly[/i], it even gets to the login screen, but it will [b][u]never[/u][/b] log me in, no, never. And I have got the IP right, I have the port right, yes I am on Hamachi, wanna know how I know all this for a fact? It lets me login on my non-jarred client. When I open the "run.bat" batch file it lets me login with that one, the jar just wont work, I asked Rob and he said something about init voids?!?! I have no idea what they are. PLease please post telling me what to do. I am not asking for a whole tutorial , please just donate 2 minutes of your time to help me and TobiasScape get back online. There [u]WILL[/u] be a reward for the first two people to help me ...[/center]
